                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p3_line",
                  "width": "42px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "（应不低于3000）；检测波长："
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p4_line",
                  "width": "36px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "nm（246nm）。特拉唑嗪峰与相邻杂质峰的分离度应符合要求。  对照品溶液制备：精密称取盐酸特拉唑嗪对照品"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p5_line",
                  "width": "63px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "mg（10mg）置"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p6_line",
                  "width": "36px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（100ml）量瓶中，加溶剂[乙腈—水—盐酸（200：800：0.9）]溶解并稀释至刻度，摇匀。再精密吸取"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p7_line",
                  "width": "49px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（5ml）置"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p8_line",
                  "width": "180px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml （25ml）量瓶中加溶剂稀释制成每1ml中约含特拉唑嗪20ug 的溶液，作为对照品溶液。供试品溶液制备：取本品1粒，将内容物倾入"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p9_line",
                  "width": "36px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（100ml）量瓶中，囊壳用溶剂分次洗净，洗液并入量瓶中，超声使盐酸特拉唑嗪溶解，用溶剂稀释至刻度，摇匀，滤过，取续滤液作为供试品溶液。"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/terazosin/finished/content_uniformity/t0_r17_c0_p10_line",
                  "width": "77px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "测定法：取续滤液 10μl注入液相色谱仪，照含量项下方法测定。按外标法以峰面积计算每粒的含量。"
                }
              ],
